                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾaślәṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 1va-67vb)&#xD;
II) Barәkännä ʾәgziʾo… “Bless us, O Lord…” (Blessing prayer) (fol. 68ra-68vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Colophon.</summary>
